## Next Steps

*   The Chairs will initiate a two-week adoption call for draft-ietf-core-core-clar-05.
*   Continue addressing the remaining issues in CoREclar, including further refining the text on DTLS RRC/CoAP Echo and the epoch/match-boxing mechanisms.
*   If the new epoch/match-boxing rules evolve into new protocol specifications beyond mere corrections, the WG will consider spinning them off into a dedicated document.